Stop for now.

21
00:01:54,540 --> 00:01:56,980
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

22
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,280
Show your warmth.

23
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:06,380
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

24
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,040
- Troupe Leader Zhu.
- Hongbing.

25
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:11,200
It's a long trip.

26
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,370
Nice to meet you again!

27
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,200
The show was so amazing!

28
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,640
I got stunned!

29
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,800
They are our key members.

30
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:18,480
Nice to meet you.

31
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,980
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

32
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,930
Come on.

33
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,040
Those are the training outfits.

34
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,080
- Find people to take them.
- Okay.

35
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,560
- Take them to the rehearsal hall.
- Sure.

36
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,000
Where are the actors?

37
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,520
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)
Inside. I'll introduce.

38
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,420
Come.

39
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,440
I've been looking forward.

40
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,680
Well, Hongbing...

41
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,760
What a car!

42
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,440
It looks better than the Magistrate's.

43
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,960
Let's welcome our distinguished guest,

44
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,480
Comrade Liu Hongbing.

45
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,720
Why did I call Comrade Liu Hongbing

46
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,120
our distinguished guest?

47
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,600
The costumes for Yang Men Nyu Jiang

48
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,960
and the fine opera armor

49
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,720
were all obtained by him

50
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,680
from various channels

51
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,160
just for us.

52
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,240
If it weren't for him

53
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:08,840
and his full support,

54
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,680
you wouldn't look so stunning on stage.

55
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,520
Impressive!

56
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,120
Today,

57
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:20,720
Comrade Liu Hongbing

58
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:24,160
came all the way from Beishan

59
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:28,120
to bring you some
brand-new practice outfits

60
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:32,000
as a reward for your amazing

61
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,000
performance.

62
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,400
Great!

63
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,840
Next up,

64
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,960
let's have Comrade Liu Hongbing

65
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,280
say a few words.

66
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,120
Welcome!

67
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,560
Hello, everyone.

68
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,840
I am a military veteran,

69
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:53,000
and here I offer you a military salute.

70
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:04,400
Helping you get these stage costumes,

71
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,480
to me,

72
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:08,080
is just a tiny matter.

73
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,240
It's not worth mentioning.

74
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,160
I've watched

75
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,320
every single show

76
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,480
of the joint performance.

77
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,480
You guys

78
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,200
deserve the most thumbs up!

79
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,560
- Thumbs up?
- You deserve a thumbs up.

80
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,480
Your speech deserves one too.

81
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,240
Feng Xiaoxiao, Liu Ke.

82
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,840
Both of you, shut up.

83
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,080
Everyone, be serious.

84
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:30,920
Applause!

85
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:48,840
Yi Qing'e?

86
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:53,200
Those are all our...

87
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,040
She's here.

88
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:55,490
- Qing'e.
- Yi Qing'e.

89
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,960
Liu Hongbing brought you something.

90
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,520
Hello, Comrade Yi Qing'e.

91
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,960
I have something for you.

92
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,360
Give me a hand.

93
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,640
Look.

94
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,240
Look.

95
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,240
Every photo in this album

96
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,040
was taken by me.

97
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,640
You were amazing.

98
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,760
This is your first show.

99
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,280
Keep it. It'll be a great memento.

100
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,000
The newspaper.

101
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:27,920
Look at this newspaper.

102
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,120
I had my friend

103
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,400
write this article just for you.

104
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,320
- Take a look.
- No, thanks.

105
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:33,440
Just take it.

106
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,280
It's a good keepsake.

107
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,560
Have a look.

108
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,760
Take it.

109
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,840
Just take it.

110
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,880
You made the front page.

111
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,280
Keep it as a souvenir.

112
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,440
Thank you.

113
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,240
So you live here?

114
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,000
Be careful!

115
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,760
How can anyone live here?

116
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,440
I want to live here.

117
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,520
We have dorms.

118
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,360
Right.

119
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:08,880
Yi Qing'e volunteered to
live here. It's convenient

120
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,760
for practice.

121
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,000
This won't do. I'm telling you,

122
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,560
living here for too long

123
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,920
will wreck her health.

124
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,560
Hongbing, you have no idea

125
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:19,080
that our troupe's housing conditions

126
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,360
are really tight.

127
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,960
I'll talk to the county leaders

128
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,160
and report this properly.

129
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,040
Such a great Qinqiang opera actress

130
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,240
deserves more attention!

131
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:30,080
Thank you so much, Hongbing.

132
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,280
You're a huge help.

133
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:33,880
- Thank you!
- On behalf of the troupe, I thank

134
00:06:34,210 --> 00:06:35,080
Liu Hongbing.

135
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,160
Thank you!

136
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,160
It's the least I could do.

137
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,480
This young man...

138
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:40,930
Oh my goodness.

139
00:06:40,930 --> 00:06:42,960
Looks young, but he's a big shot.

140
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,800
He carries himself like a soldier.

141
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,960
Really?

142
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,040
He does.

143
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,960
Go serve it.

144
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,800
Okay, okay.

145
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,120
- Careful.
- Coming!

146
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:58,000
The troupe's own canteen.

147
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,720
Nothing fancy. Have a taste.

148
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,280
Tomato and egg.

149
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,760
How does it taste?

150
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,600
Great!

151
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:05,800
Listen,

152
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,520
the food here

153
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:10,680
is amazing. Just like army food.

154
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,560
You have quite the palate.

155
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,160
Our cook, Master Song,

156
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,960
used to serve in the mess squad.

157
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,160
He was a squad leader.

158
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,400
Then I must toast him.

159
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,800
Plump.

160
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:23,080
Take Hongbing to chat with Master Song.

161
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,560
Hello, Master Song.

162
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,240
He drives for the leaders of

163
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,840
the Administrative Office.

164
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,080
Why drag me to this dinner?

165
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:38,000
Why? For your own matter, of course.

166
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,840
What matter?

167
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,320
He's got strong connections.

168
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,680
I want to get you back to the troupe.

169
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,280
He's just a driver.

170
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:46,840
Can he pull that off?

171
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,680
He can.

172
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,960
Do you know what his father does?

173
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,320
What? A county leader?

174
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,480
Administrative Commissioner.

175
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,120
Liu Hongbing may not be highly educated,

176
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:01,080
but he's a passionate guy who loves to help.

177
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:03,440
That newspaper article about Qing'e.

178
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,880
He's the one who got someone to write it.

179
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,720
Did you ask him to do it?

180
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,240
He did it on his own.

181
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,920
What does it have to do with him?

182
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,120
Why would he do that?

183
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,760
He values talent and did it for us.

184
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,880
Our girl in "Yang Men Nyu Jiang"...

185
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,320
Wasn't her singing amazing?

186
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,560
Truly remarkable.

187
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,600
Such talent deserves great coverage.

188
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,760
Right?

189
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,400
Just chatted with my buddy.

190
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,960
He served eight years before me.

191
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,680
An old squad leader.

192
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,860
- Close as family.
- Yes indeed.

193
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,960
Wherever you soldiers go,

194
00:08:28,960 --> 00:08:29,840
you're all like one big family.

195
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,680
Absolutely.

196
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,920
True comrades-in-arms.

197
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,440
Aunt Plump just told me that

198
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,160
Qing'e is

199
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,480
a talent raised in this cafeteria.

200
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,320
What's the story?

201
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:46,440
I guess you could say that.

202
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:50,280
Qing'e owes where she is today all to him.

203
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,120
Him?

204
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,480
I told you about Hu Sanyuan.

205
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,040
I didn't tell you

206
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,040
about his relationship with Qing'e.

207
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,000
Hu Sanyuan is Yi Qing'e's uncle.

208
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,840
Her real uncle.

209
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,000
Uncle?

210
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,720
So you're the uncle!

211
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,480
Nice to meet you.

212
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,600
I've heard so much about you.

213
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,080
She was amazing on stage.

214
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,800
A truly rare talent.

215
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,280
Hongbing.

216
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,720
Sit, sit.

217
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,480
I've heard so much about you.

218
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:26,360
That year, Hu Sanyuan went to prison.

219
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:28,720
Yi Qing'e was implicated.

220
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,400
My predecessor

221
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,600
wanted to fire her.

222
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,520
I tried everything I could

223
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:35,480
to keep her working in the kitchen.

224
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,920
Qing'e is a tough one.

225
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,440
A few masters in our troupe

226
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,840
saw her talent for opera

227
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:44,400
and secretly took her in as a student.

228
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:47,160
She learned while tending the fire.

229
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:49,000
That's how she got so good today.

230
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,960
It wasn't easy.

231
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,840
It's so touching.

232
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:54,640
With such a touching story,

233
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,560
why didn't you write it in the paper?

234
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,800
I have an idea.

235
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,680
You'll be going to perform

236
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:01,880
in Beishan for a month.

237
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:03,600
I'll ask my friends in the press

238
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,480
to do a proper interview with Qing'e.

239
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,000
We'll put these touching stories

240
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,520
all over the newspapers,

241
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,280
so everyone can read about it.

242
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,480
As for this...

243
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,520
let's not report it.

244
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,520
Why not?

245
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,960
I'll explain it to you later.

246
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,440
Alright.

247
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,800
Then call Qing'e over.

248
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,120
Let's toast her.

249
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,080
The show was such a success.

250
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,240
It's worth celebrating.

251
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,000
Our troupe has rules.

252
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,480
Members are forbidden from drinking.

253
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,440
Especially female members.

254
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,640
They can't drink with guests.

255
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:31,640
I'll drink with you.

256
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,880
Rules? Understood.

257
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,240
Understood.

258
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:41,480
To get Hu Sanyuan back to our troupe,

259
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,440
is it difficult?

260
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:46,000
That's no big deal.

261
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,000
Uncle,

262
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:49,040
I'm not bragging to you,

263
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,240
but for me, this matter

264
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,360
is just a tiny thing.

265
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,520
But why return to the county troupe?

266
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,560
I can pull some strings

267
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:57,080
to get you and Qing'e

268
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,720
into the Local Troupe together.

269
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,440
I asked you to bring him back,

270
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,920
and you're poaching my staff?

271
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,120
That's not what I meant.

272
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,640
Qing'e deserves a bigger stage.

273
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,160
That's not gonna happen. Our troupe

274
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,560
just got back on its feet.

275
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,320
The old masters either died or left.

276
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,120
We just trained two girls well.

277
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,280
The Provincial Troupe poached them.

278
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:15,120
Qing'e is our key trainee now. If she

279
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,760
leaves, we're done for.

280
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:19,080
Look at the bigger picture.

281
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,000
What bigger picture?

282
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,760
You two stop caring about my business.

283
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:23,560
I won't go back to the troupe.

284
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,400
Why not?

285
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,960
No reason. I just don't want to.

286
