On par with the County Magistrate?

570
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:42,080
Huang Zhengjing and Zhu Jiru report to you.

571
00:25:53,120 --> 00:25:54,240
What's this?

572
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,840
(Veggies, soup, Mo)

573
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:57,200
I drew it in my free time.

574
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,280
Just to kill time.

575
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,400
(Serving food, making tofu)
Nice sheep drawing.

576
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:39,720
Of course.

577
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:45,120
Serving food, making tofu.

578
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:48,400
An old geezer sits by the pot.

579
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,360
Wants to eat

580
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:53,120
a bowl

581
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:54,200
of tofu.

582
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,520
You even know Pinyin.

583
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:12,340
(Beishan Theater)

584
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,120
The Yang Men Nyu Jiang show

585
00:27:19,120 --> 00:27:21,040
was a massive success.

586
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,920
During the regional showcase,

587
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,960
after taking first place,

588
00:27:25,360 --> 00:27:26,320
the local leaders

589
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:28,320
had them stationed in Beishan

590
00:27:28,320 --> 00:27:30,080
to perform for half a year.

591
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:34,560
The name Yi Qing'e in the Beishan area

592
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:37,520
was recognized everywhere.

593
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:46,680
Bravo!

594
00:27:48,840 --> 00:27:49,760
Yi Qing'e.

595
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,480
Let's talk about your past.

596
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,600
Maybe your childhood.

597
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:54,760
Things from my childhood...

598
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,640
I don't really remember.

599
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,640
Have some Kvass. It's refreshing.

600
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,880
Some for our reporter friend too.

601
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:03,600
No, thanks.

602
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:06,760
I'll leave it here in case you get thirsty.

603
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:22,680
Bravo!

604
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:26,000
- Bravo!
- Your breathtaking,

605
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:28,240
gorgeous face

606
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:31,560
pierced through many unreachable,

607
00:28:31,560 --> 00:28:32,680
solid barriers.

608
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:48,000
You're clearly a Song
dynasty snake spirit,

609
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,120
yet you make...

610
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,520
Bravo!

611
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:13,000
Bravo!

612
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:18,680
Yi Qing'e!

613
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:20,240
Yi Qing'e!

614
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:25,480
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)
Beishan Regional News.

615
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,960
(Huge success)
Your Yang Men Nyu Jiang photo

616
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,320
takes up half a page.

617
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:31,800
And also...

618
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:33,160
Look.

619
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:37,800
I used color film just for
your photos. They can't

620
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:40,080
even develop them in Beishan.

621
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:42,680
I went all the way to Chang'an for this.

622
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:43,520
Every single one...

623
00:29:45,080 --> 00:29:47,120
- Sorry.
- Watch where you're going.

624
00:29:47,120 --> 00:29:47,960
Didn't notice.

625
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:49,520
Look.

626
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:51,640
Look at you...

627
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:53,280
Hey, buddy!

628
00:29:54,080 --> 00:29:55,600
Watch where you're going!

629
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:57,200
Why keep doing this? What's your problem?

630
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,200
You're in my way.

631
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:00,000
In your way? Who are you?

632
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:02,160
This is a dressing room, not a commune.

633
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:03,160
Get out.

634
00:30:03,320 --> 00:30:04,520
What? Doing this on purpose?

635
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:05,620
- I do it on purpose.
- You...

636
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:07,840
I'll teach you

637
00:30:08,160 --> 00:30:09,000
a lesson!

638
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,400
Stop fighting!

639
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,680
We're not fighting.

640
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:14,640
We're taking off makeup.

641
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,040
You shouldn't be backstage.

642
00:30:18,280 --> 00:30:19,120
Well...

643
00:30:19,320 --> 00:30:22,600
I just came to hand out photos.

644
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:23,640
Look.

645
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:25,400
Photos of everyone. Look.

646
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:27,440
I got one of you too.

647
00:30:27,650 --> 00:30:28,620
Here, take it.

648
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,400
What are you looking at back there?

649
00:30:33,360 --> 00:30:35,080
Don't be so petty.

650
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:36,960
He's weird. Come on.

651
00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:38,320
Hand these out to everyone.

652
00:30:39,080 --> 00:30:41,080
Qing'e, you're famous now!

653
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,000
And look at this.

654
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:45,880
Our local Beishan Evening News.

655
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,240
Everyone gets one.

656
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:48,640
Take a look.

657
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,680
Beishan's Yang Men Nyu Jiang show

658
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:51,760
was a huge success!

659
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:53,320
Here, one for each of you. Look.

660
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,520
- Your play...
- Yi Qing'e.

661
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:56,720
- Half a page in the news!
- Let me see!

662
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:58,200
Come look!

663
00:30:58,480 --> 00:31:00,080
Don't fight over it. Stop.

664
00:31:00,080 --> 00:31:01,280
Here, here, I have more!

665
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:02,240
Come here, hurry!

666
00:31:02,240 --> 00:31:03,080
Looking great.

667
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,360
- Here, take these.
- I gotta say,

668
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:07,320
he's a pretty good photographer.

669
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:08,280
This one is great.

670
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:09,960
His skills aren't bad.

671
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,320
Qing'e.

672
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:13,680
Come with me.

673
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:35,840
I just received a notice.

674
00:31:37,040 --> 00:31:38,880
Report to Provincial Qinqiang Troupe ASAP.

675
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,200
Why?

676
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,120
I don't know.

677
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:47,160
I'm not going.

678
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:48,560
It's not up to you.

679
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:50,440
Or me.

680
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:53,120
A top provincial leader

681
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:55,720
called the County Party Secretary.

682
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:57,800
You have to go.

683
00:31:58,280 --> 00:31:59,480
I'm not going anywhere.

684
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:02,320
Master died right here.

685
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:04,960
I only sing right here.

686
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:07,360
I sing for my master.

687
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:14,880
Even if he were alive, it still

688
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:15,880
wouldn't be up to you!

689
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,840
I'm not going!

690
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:27,240
The performance plan has changed.

691
00:32:28,080 --> 00:32:29,440
Pack your bags. Tomorrow,

692
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:30,720
we'll head back.

693
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:32,920
What are you whining about?

694
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:33,880
Go pack your bags!

695
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:34,920
What are you waiting for?

696
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:36,680
Go.

697
00:33:11,260 --> 00:33:17,020
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

698
00:33:17,020 --> 00:33:23,820
(Boiled water)

699
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:25,880
Master Song.

700
00:33:26,050 --> 00:33:26,960
Where is she?

701
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:27,920
In her room.

702
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:41,560
You...

703
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:42,400
Work.

704
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:43,760
I want to go see her.

705
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,880
I'm her uncle. Stay out of it.

706
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:48,960
Qing'e.

707
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:51,000
Qing'e.

708
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:58,600
What's wrong?

709
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,360
Zhu Jiru told me everything.

710
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,120
There's nothing we can do, right?

711
00:34:18,120 --> 00:34:20,440
The higher-ups summoned you.

712
00:34:21,160 --> 00:34:22,680
No one can stop them.

713
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,840
I know what you're thinking.

714
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:30,800
The Opera Troupe trained you.

715
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:33,160
The Opera Troupe needs your help right now.

716
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:34,800
If you leave now,

717
00:34:36,200 --> 00:34:37,080
it just doesn't feel right.

718
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:40,640
But there's no other way now, is there?

719
00:34:42,560 --> 00:34:44,480
Sometimes we just don't have a choice.

720
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:51,800
But have you thought about it?

721
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:56,160
If your master were here...

722
00:34:57,640 --> 00:34:58,800
If Master Gou were here,

723
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:00,960
what would he say?

724
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:04,720
He'd definitely tell you to go.

725
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,880
The Provincial Qinqiang Troupe is where

726
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:10,600
Qinqiang opera singers dream of going.

727
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:15,760
A bigger stage means a bigger show.

728
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,240
You have the talent now.

729
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,960
This county troupe is

730
00:35:30,560 --> 00:35:32,000
too small for you.

731
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:37,640
Did you hear me?

732
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:41,000
Are you listening to me?

733
00:35:46,680 --> 00:35:47,680
I'm scared.

734
00:35:49,640 --> 00:35:50,800
Scared of what?

735
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:54,200
When I first came here as a kid,

736
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:55,920
I was scared for years.

737
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:01,280
Actually, my bravery was all an act.

738
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,320
Now I'm finally not scared anymore.

739
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:05,440
You want me to leave.

740
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:10,200
I don't want to live in fear anymore.

741
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:13,480
I... I get it.

742
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:16,440
Back then

743
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,600
when I was sent away,

744
00:36:18,600 --> 00:36:19,520
I didn't want to go either.

745
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:20,560
I was scared too.

746
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:22,720
No use.

747
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:26,880
I stayed a while and settled down.

748
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:28,680
Then I wasn't scared anymore.

749
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,760
To tell you the truth,

750
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:32,560
I was scared again when I got out.

751
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,680
What was I supposed to do?

752
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:38,160
How to face people?

753
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,160
But I got through it.

754
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:45,280
We face a lot in this life.

755
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,280
We have to keep moving forward.

756
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,960
Once you get through it and look back,

757
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:51,920
you'll see it was nothing at all.

758
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,960
Don't worry, I will go with you.

759
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:02,920
I've cleaned up my act.

760
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,440
I'm not as hot-tempered.

761
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,840
I won't cause trouble for you.

762
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:13,080
Master Gu is already there.

763
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,360
He can look out for you.

764
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,680
You have to listen to Master Gou.

765
00:37:20,720 --> 00:37:21,960
He definitely wants you to go.

766
00:37:47,720 --> 00:37:49,120
You like Yi Qing'e, don't you?

767
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:52,720
I do.

768
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:56,120
I know.

769
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:58,000
She likes you too.

770
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,480
What do we do now?

771
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:32,520
Understand?

772
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:36,040
You could crush me like a bug.

773
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:38,360
Why would I crush you?

774
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,960
There are two ways to like someone.

775
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,080
One is to hold it tight.

776
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,600
The tighter you hold, the sooner it dies.

777
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:48,840
And the other?

778
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:50,440
Just let it go.

779
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:51,920
Let it fly.

780
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:54,560
Into the vast sky.

781
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:55,920
Just let it fly.

782
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:08,520
Got it?

783
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:14,560
If not, think it over carefully.

784
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:41,160
What did my uncle tell you?

785
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:43,680
He said you're dumb.

786
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:45,840
I'm not.

787
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:48,000
People used to say you were dumb.

788
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:48,840
I didn't think so.

789
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:50,800
Now I think you're dumb.

790
00:39:51,520 --> 00:39:52,800
Still saying you're not?

791
00:39:53,680 --> 00:39:54,840
Then why skip Provincial Qinqiang Troupe?

792
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,480
I want to go.

793
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,360
I'll get into the Provincial Qinqiang Troupe

794
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,600
and leave this mountain valley.

795
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:07,600
You head there first.

796
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:09,720
Settle in and wait for me.

797
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:23,520
If you leave, they might cancel the play.

798
00:40:33,660 --> 00:40:34,600
Look.

799
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:42,300
Is it nice?

800
00:40:45,560 --> 00:40:46,430
It is.

801
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:08,120
For a silkworm to become a butterfly,

802
00:41:08,520 --> 00:41:11,000
it must survive countless hardships.

803
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:14,360
How bitter it is, what it truly feels like,

804
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:17,360
only the butterfly itself knows.

805
00:41:17,530 --> 00:41:18,440
I understand that.

806
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:20,360
I once raised silkworms.

807
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,840
You're raising one again.

808
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:25,200
So are Gou Cunzhong,

809
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:26,800
Cunchao, the others…

810
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:30,480
We're all doing our best to turn this kid

811
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:33,000
into a beautiful butterfly.

812
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:36,480
"Fierce the west wind,

813
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:41,320
wild geese cry beneath
the frost-lit dawn moon.

814
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,280
Beneath that frosty moon,

815
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:49,160
hoofbeats scatter,
bugles choke in the night.

816
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:53,320
The mighty pass stretches on, hard as iron."

817
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,360
Chairman Mao's

818
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:57,360
Yi Qin'e · Loushan Pass.

819
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,520
Fits this moment perfectly.

820
00:42:00,560 --> 00:42:01,520
Yi Qing'e?

821
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:04,120
Yi Qin'e

822
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,560
is an old ci-poetry tune title.

823
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,720
Li Qingzhao and Li Bai

824
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:10,440
both wrote

825
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:13,680
immortal lines under that title.

826
00:42:15,440 --> 00:42:16,440
"Yi" means remembrance.

827
00:42:17,120 --> 00:42:18,120
"Qin", the Qin Mountains.

828
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:20,360
"E"… the same "E" from Yi Qing'e.

829
00:42:25,240 --> 00:42:27,800
How about we use Yi Qin'e

830
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:30,680
as the kid's stage name?

831
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:32,680
Good. You tell her.

832
00:42:34,340 --> 00:42:35,230
Kid!

833
00:42:37,050 --> 00:42:37,990
Kid.

834
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,880
You're about to set off.

835
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,480
Your uncle and I want

836
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:44,800
to give you a stage name.

837
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,880
It may bring you good luck.

838
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:52,000
Yi Qin'e is an old ci-poetry tune title.

839
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:54,280
You can also think of it as meaning

840
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:57,160
"a woman of Qin who sings opera".

841
00:42:58,200 --> 00:42:59,680
From now on, your name is Yi Qin'e.

842
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:06,940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

843
00:43:09,040 --> 00:43:10,560
I have your word.

844
00:43:10,560 --> 00:43:11,720
Get into the Provincial Troupe.

845
00:43:12,860 --> 00:43:14,040
Qin'e!

846
00:43:14,260 --> 00:43:15,320
A ghost that won't go away?

847
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:18,920
"He was the root of disaster."

848
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:21,560
Watch your accents!

849
00:43:21,680 --> 00:43:23,360
Let her rest for a bit?

850
00:43:23,360 --> 00:43:24,400
I can fill in.

851
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:25,370
No dormitory?

852
00:43:25,460 --> 00:43:26,470
(Ice Pops, Shuipen Yangrou)

853
00:43:27,050 --> 00:43:27,950
Qin'e!

854
00:43:28,200 --> 00:43:29,040
Opera tickets!

855
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:41,620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

856
00:43:43,090 --> 00:43:47,930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

857
00:43:49,370 --> 00:43:53,560
♪We met and brushed past♪

858
00:43:55,120 --> 00:44:02,420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

859
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:20,540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

860
00:44:22,140 --> 00:44:27,710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

861
00:44:28,830 --> 00:44:32,890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

862
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:39,610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

863
00:44:40,770 --> 00:44:44,970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

864
00:44:46,010 --> 00:44:51,640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

865
00:44:52,810 --> 00:44:57,500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

866
00:44:58,180 --> 00:45:03,350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

867
00:45:04,020 --> 00:45:09,050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

868
00:45:10,080 --> 00:45:15,510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

869
00:45:15,890 --> 00:45:21,170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

870
00:45:22,120 --> 00:45:27,930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

871
00:45:27,930 --> 00:45:33,350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

872
00:45:33,900 --> 00:45:39,410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

873
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:44,920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

874
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:51,220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

875
00:45:52,020 --> 00:46:01,050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪

